{"id": "ChIJu948xPZ9hYARMOy-BUTq8pE", "rating": 4.5, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_MODERATE", "userRatingCount": 6024, "displayName": {"text": "Fentons Creamery", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "A retro ice cream parlor known for their large sundaes and cones and their large variety of flavors.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJu948xPZ9hYARMOy-BUTq8pE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xwSFExRnNVa3BHYUVGaVJuTnplVFZOTjBoVVZXYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Have seating outside but no service. But they are more than accommodating with allowing you to just get take out option and sit outside. Plenty of good diner food options and loads of ice cream flavors. Be aware the scoop sizes are pretty large. I got a half ice cream sandwich by just getting a cookie and a scoop on top, because the normal ice cream sandwich has to scoops.\n\nThe fries and onion rings were just ok, but the ranch dip was pretty good. My friends enjoyed their burgers, saying the gherkin was especially tasty l.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Have seating outside but no service. But they are more than accommodating with allowing you to just get take out option and sit outside. Plenty of good diner food options and loads of ice cream flavors. Be aware the scoop sizes are pretty large. I got a half ice cream sandwich by just getting a cookie and a scoop on top, because the normal ice cream sandwich has to scoops.\n\nThe fries and onion rings were just ok, but the ranch dip was pretty good. My friends enjoyed their burgers, saying the gherkin was especially tasty l.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Joanna", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106427429597578957027/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXWbv8ibFIWGBh-2GOr6KlFlYYjVFFCPohyuKhecoCJYiyEQcTz=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-08T14:55:22.579066029Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xwSFExRnNVa3BHYUVGaVJuTnplVFZOTjBoVVZXYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xwSFExRnNVa3BHYUVGaVJuTnplVFZOTjBoVVZXYxAB!2m1!1s0x80857df6c43cdebb:0x91f2ea4405beec30"}, {"name": "places/ChIJu948xPZ9hYARMOy-BUTq8pE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25ST1RtRmFVWFprTkRWNGFHSlJiVmxUU2xKWU0xRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "The ice cream and the lace are so magical the staff team members are all so dedicated to the customers. It really brings me back to when I was 6 years old and went to the ice cream parlor very much like this with my parents,  I feel excited like a little kid any time I'm going there. Whatever you ask from the very diverse menu will be totally awesome. My favorite is the ice cream soda but anything, anything you want will be great. They have mostly classic flavors,  if you are looking for the exotic or unusual there are other places I can recommend but if you want a wholesome classic ice cream experience,  this is your bet.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "The ice cream and the lace are so magical the staff team members are all so dedicated to the customers. It really brings me back to when I was 6 years old and went to the ice cream parlor very much like this with my parents,  I feel excited like a little kid any time I'm going there. Whatever you ask from the very diverse menu will be totally awesome. My favorite is the ice cream soda but anything, anything you want will be great. They have mostly classic flavors,  if you are looking for the exotic or unusual there are other places I can recommend but if you want a wholesome classic ice cream experience,  this is your bet.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Hernan Vargas", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/115872439278890744571/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVGGKXQKccI_wHTOhPBuexNqQvipyJP5W8wcRb0raFbWoyZV7h8=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-09T04:57:48.412219307Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25ST1RtRmFVWFprTkRWNGFHSlJiVmxUU2xKWU0xRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25ST1RtRmFVWFprTkRWNGFHSlJiVmxUU2xKWU0xRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857df6c43cdebb:0x91f2ea4405beec30"}, {"name": "places/ChIJu948xPZ9hYARMOy-BUTq8pE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pRMVNUQjZSak5WZVRKbmNXdHlNbVZNZGs5NGNXYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "The ice cream is legendary, but if I’m being honest, the service usually sucks. I get my ice cream to go because the servers rarely get the order right, and they seem bothered to have to serve you. My all time favorite ice cream is their toasted almond. If you love hot caramel on your ice cream, they have some of the best here. It’s definitely worth a stop, just dine in at your own risk.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "The ice cream is legendary, but if I’m being honest, the service usually sucks. I get my ice cream to go because the servers rarely get the order right, and they seem bothered to have to serve you. My all time favorite ice cream is their toasted almond. If you love hot caramel on your ice cream, they have some of the best here. It’s definitely worth a stop, just dine in at your own risk.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Ro C.", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113591027041979666082/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXEODf7uVs9s8SwH9KNUqtul1wURznON-gDvOsDyEftPlCAYfdJ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-04T06:21:58.115263887Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pRMVNUQjZSak5WZVRKbmNXdHlNbVZNZGs5NGNXYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pRMVNUQjZSak5WZVRKbmNXdHlNbVZNZGs5NGNXYxAB!2m1!1s0x80857df6c43cdebb:0x91f2ea4405beec30"}, {"name": "places/ChIJu948xPZ9hYARMOy-BUTq8pE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xVd1gxVTNNbk5uZFRsSVIwRlZVMFZsUzB0dVdIYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "BLT phenomenal! Sourdough buttered and toasted perfectly. Bacon slightly thick, but crispy. The lettuce was crisp, tomatoes were a smidge over ripened. Large portion sizes on everything I saw the wait staff bring out. Large selection of Icecream options, also generously served. Restaurant extremely crowded and loud. The wait staff is amazing; excellent knowledgeable of the menu, they work together (doesn’t matter who the assigned wait person is, they help out), good old fashioned customer service.\n\nParking is horrible.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "BLT phenomenal! Sourdough buttered and toasted perfectly. Bacon slightly thick, but crispy. The lettuce was crisp, tomatoes were a smidge over ripened. Large portion sizes on everything I saw the wait staff bring out. Large selection of Icecream options, also generously served. Restaurant extremely crowded and loud. The wait staff is amazing; excellent knowledgeable of the menu, they work together (doesn’t matter who the assigned wait person is, they help out), good old fashioned customer service.\n\nParking is horrible.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "K Anderson", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110294297919899261631/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIXmhOnypjM1wM7ojwOMOyGPquHhbDa6Jvtqx36KavJECKClQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2025-12-28T20:33:30.801145454Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xVd1gxVTNNbk5uZFRsSVIwRlZVMFZsUzB0dVdIYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xVd1gxVTNNbk5uZFRsSVIwRlZVMFZsUzB0dVdIYxAB!2m1!1s0x80857df6c43cdebb:0x91f2ea4405beec30"}, {"name": "places/ChIJu948xPZ9hYARMOy-BUTq8pE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s5cVZGcHdZVXB3TmxkTmRYcGFObTVyWDJneFQyYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Fentons is great big space with just classically great flavors. They have all the classics plus a bunch of fun flavors. It’s not salt and straw crazy but tons of really good options.\n\nI got a cherry ice cream that was just great. Worth going to.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Fentons is great big space with just classically great flavors. They have all the classics plus a bunch of fun flavors. It’s not salt and straw crazy but tons of really good options.\n\nI got a cherry ice cream that was just great. Worth going to.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Paul", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114081654695003926529/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVsOIcoVoVSjXdCfRqaH6Z3cYFLhXTASTibSVH8CXp_FhJBB7fj=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-06T05:30:18.155847346Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s5cVZGcHdZVXB3TmxkTmRYcGFObTVyWDJneFQyYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s5cVZGcHdZVXB3TmxkTmRYcGFObTVyWDJneFQyYxAB!2m1!1s0x80857df6c43cdebb:0x91f2ea4405beec30"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJu948xPZ9hYARMOy-BUTq8pE/photos/AWCwydj17p_juvJOppwSkGnSkFvwt2eSKNL0C47mqXZQWcGyJYPoRzkubc5uVpAxsabujdFGQ-cTS7J-CakwX_Jg1W4uwHJuJ9LvhvEtVXnsmsK3SDmCypBPjvIxjZv-oi_XUnFd-frugTGXfjRT4Mtm-JdW-ye1OkDIcBjJg6daIFEYlaqKxhpjLAsFiq